% if (!$guide) {$guide = 'guidelines';}

<p>The uploading of QTL data needs to be done in one session. 
  Therefore, prepare your data files in the required format before 
  starting the process. Please read the submission <% lc($guide) %> first. If you 
  would like to have the formatting of your dataset checked 
  beforehand, send your data to: <a href=mailto:iyt2\@cornell.edu>iyt2@cornell.edu</a>.
</p> 
        
<p>Required data:</p>
       
<ul>
  <li>Some basic information about the population,</li>
  <li>Traits data file (tab delimited),</li>
  <li>Phenotype data file (tab delimited),</li> 
  <li>Genotype data file (tab delimited) and</li> 
  <li>Statistical parameters.</li>
  <li><i>Markers with their sequences need to be already in SGN. 
      Read <a href="/cview/help/map_submission">here</a> on how 
      to submit markers to SGN.
  </i>
</ul>

